title: rounded tech sans Parental ID "Advisory - Gangst"
content:
Searching for this type. Thought it is Magda but it isn't. Any Ideas?

author: jawbox

comments.content: Looks like a [Lineto](http://web.archive.org/web/20150126052738/http:/www.lineto.com/) typeface, but I checked out all the fonts on their site and didn't find an exact match; Autoscape is pretty close, though.
Arrgh -- it's so close to [Arame](http://web.archive.org/web/20150126052738/http:/www.myfonts.com/fonts/dimitrelima/0arame/) I can taste it, but it's not exact!
I thought also that this is a Lineto-Font. Any other ideas?

I know this is an old thread but Ginobcn found this one [in this thread](http://web.archive.org/web/20150126052738/http:/www.typophile.com/node/41207). It's from NeubauLaden and called [Neu Baubet (NB55RMS)](http://web.archive.org/web/20150126052738/http:/www.neubauladen.com/product/1037).
